OL,3,CSir Jim Ratcliffe 'total
OL,4,Cembarrassment' after immigration
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FManchester United's most prominent
OL,8,Fsupporters' group has called Sir Jim
OL,9,FRatcliffe a "total embarrassment"
OL,10,Fafter he said the UK is "colonised by
OL,11,Fimmigrants".
OL,13,FThe 1958 Group released a lengthy
OL,14,Fstatement describing the club's co-
OL,15,Fowner's comments as "very ill-
OL,16,Fadvised", and said he should not be
OL,17,F"commenting on the issues of our
OL,18,Fcountry while living in Monaco to
OL,19,Favoid paying tax".
