OL,4,Cembarrassment' after immigration
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,FThe billionaire told Sky News on
OL,8,FWednesday that the UK was spending too
OL,9,Fmuch money on immigration and
OL,10,Fsuggested the Prime Minister was "too
OL,11,Fnice" to do "difficult things" to
OL,12,Fstabilise the country's economy.
OL,14,FThe owner of one of the world's
OL,15,Flargest chemical companies, Ineos,
OL,16,Fsaid: "You can't have an economy with
OL,17,Fnine million people on benefits and
OL,18,Fhuge levels of immigrants coming in.
OL,26,@xD@GOU
