OL,3,CSir Jim Ratcliffe 'total
OL,4,Cembarrassment' after immigration
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"I mean, the UK is being colonised.
OL,8,FIt's costing too much money. The UK
OL,9,Fhas been colonised by immigrants."
OL,11,FSir Jim's comments have been met with
OL,12,Fbacklash from across the political and
OL,13,Fsporting world, with the Prime
OL,14,FMinister himself describing the
OL,15,Fbillionaire businessmen's remarks as
OL,16,F"offensive" - and called on him to
OL,17,Fapologise.
