OL,3,CSir Jim Ratcliffe 'total
OL,4,Cembarrassment' after immigration
OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"At a time when hate crime is rising
OL,8,Fand communities are feeling
OL,9,Fincreasingly unsafe, public figures
OL,10,Fmust recognise the weight and
OL,11,Fconsequences of their words.
OL,13,F"Britain is a diverse society shaped
OL,14,Fby migration. Framing that diversity
OL,15,Fas 'colonisation' is reinforcing
OL,16,Fharmful stereotypes and emboldening
OL,17,Fthose who seek to divide rather than
OL,18,Funite."
