OL,7,FElsewhere, Kick It Out - the anti-
OL,8,Fdiscrimination football campaign group
OL,9,F- criticised his comments, including
OL,10,Fthe claim that the UK population has
OL,11,Fswelled by 12 million since 2020.
OL,13,FIn a statement it said: "Sir Jim
OL,14,FRatcliffe's comments are disgraceful
OL,15,Fand deeply divisive at a time when
OL,16,Ffootball does so much to bring
OL,17,Fcommunities together.
