OL,5,Ccomments
OL,7,F"In addition to the inaccurate figures
OL,8,Fmentioned, it's worth reminding him
OL,9,Fthat Manchester United has a diverse
OL,10,Ffan base and plays in a city whose
OL,11,Fcultural history has been enriched by
OL,12,Fimmigrants.
OL,14,F"This type of language and leadership
OL,15,Fhas no place in English football, and
OL,16,Fwe believe most fans will feel the
OL,17,Fsame."
